For example, change assert in
```scala
1810	        if (flatname == nme.EMPTY) {
1811	          assert(rawowner.isClass)
1812	          flatname = newTypeName(compactify(rawowner.name.toString() + "$$" + rawname))
1813	        }
```
to
```scala
assert(rawowner.isClass, (initName, rawname, rawowner))
```
